messageBody:
There is a new file in the files location of this list called
"TestCoverageUtility.zip".

This file was posted as a follow-up to some discussions earlier on in the
"best practices" thread.

The tool works with the VAJ tools environment to determine whether the
classes in the selected package(s)/project(s) have tests associated with
them.

I am open to suggestions and a little bit of criticism. Too much criticism
is not welcome as I have included a disclaimer that this tool is the product
of a two day proof-of-concept :).

-Jason
